[b]Typeface[/b]
OpenDyslexic: a free, dyslexia-friendly font.
[url=https://opendyslexic.org]opendyslexic.org[/url]

[b]Chess engine[/b]
Stockfish (GPL-3.0).

[b]Quotes[/b]
Savielly Tartakower, Emanuel Lasker, Johannes Zukertort, Paul Morphy.

[b]Built with[/b]
Godot Engine (MIT). [url=https://godotengine.org]godotengine.org[/url]

